Task 7: Secure Web Hosting
Bash

dnf install httpd -y
sed -i 's/Listen 80/Listen 8181/' /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf
echo "Welcome to RHEL 10" > /var/www/html/index.html
semanage port -a -t httpd_port_t -p tcp 8181
firewall-cmd --permanent --add-port=8181/tcp
firewall-cmd --reload
systemctl enable --now httpd
Task 8: Autofs
Bash

